	<h1 class="title">匈牙利还没加入欧元区，货币就被设计好了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4469/small/4469.jpg?1421125271" alt="">
